更知自己想要/需要咩，可以係最適合嘅舞台搏盡表現<br />\n改變命運嘅唔係多咗張沙紙，而係自己進化咗<br />\n祝你順利<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef249661885880272f8c690b6d16d21fdd79ddd1","tid":838053,"uid":158832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T17:44:12.000Z","msg":"Gpa咁高，可以諗下master或者經non ju transfer<br />\n科目接近都可以exempt倒至多一年（好似係）"}]}